snippet.title: ClashMon: Ignition Game Trailer
snippet.description:
FREE-to-play ClashMon: Ignition is a browser-based Web3 collectible battle RPG that lets players build up their monster decks by collecting or trading ClashMon heroes.

Players can duke it out in PvP battles on Arena or Championship mode, and they can also earn TORCH, the game’s utility token, through fishing.
